python-spiderfoot (Python OSINT tool)

SpiderFoot is an open source intelligence (OSINT) automation tool.
It integrates with just about every data source available and utilises
a range of methods for data analysis, making that data easy to
navigate.

HOME: https://github.com/smicallef/spiderfoot

======================================================================
REQUIRES: python-adblockparser python-beautifulsoup4 python-cherrypy-cors python-cryptography python-exifread python-ipwhois python-netaddr python-networkx python-openpyxl python-phonenumbers python-publicsuffixlist python-pygexf python-pygexf python-pyopenssl python-pyopenssl python-pypdf2 python-pysocks python-python-docx python-secure python-whois 

